text: Khlebodarovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Yumaguzinsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 69 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 42 km from Mrakovo, 12 km from Yumaguzino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Khlebodarovka, Kugarchinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
